# MOCK PLACEHOLDER for the conformance operations file.
#
# Real operations file (format follows the reference implementation; YAML or
# similar readable format with comments preferred) will list, for each test:
#   - the operation (union, intersect, difference, symmetric_difference,
#     insert, hash)
#   - the input graph(s) by id
#   - the expected hash of the result
#
# Example shape (illustrative only):
#
#   - op: union
#     inputs: [g001, g002]
#     expected_hash: <multihash-string>
#
#   - op: hash
#     input: g001
#     expected_hash: <multihash-string>
#
# An implementation conforms iff every operation's computed hash matches the
# expected_hash. No partial conformance.
